{"tid":1856891,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[睇完#1先好問] 網購外科口罩集中討論96","createTime":"2020-02-02T01:11:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T03:08:01.000Z","uid":119810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ab8fdd808a0b33ce5c4e8dfd09e357b73324e163","tid":1856891,"uid":119810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T01:11:09.000Z","msg":"<em><strong>內容及資料僅供參考，投資涉及風險，口罩價格可升亦可跌，甚至變成亳無價值。旅客在決定是否購買有關口罩之前應先閱讀有關風險評估，以了解該建議發售之詳細資料，並應就本身的財務、其他狀況及需要，詳細考慮並決定購買有關口罩是否切合本身特定的需要，若有需要更應咨詢其他專業意見，方可作出有關購買決定。<br />\n忠告：親自買罩 咪俾錢炒狗[b]</em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本上而家得返日本Amazon重有口罩賣，<br />\n所以唔好買太多，到時禁運真係攬炒就一鑊熟。<br />\n問呢個得唔得嘅，最少睇曬前2/3個post嘅圖。<br />\n做開團團長嘅，求下你，你開個tg,wts gp出嚟畀人join，夠數就關link。<br />\n間間集運都爆，唔好再問邊間快啲邊間好用，根本就無人知。<br />\n記得留意返集運公司對體積重收費同要求，隨時運費貴過口罩本身，重有拒收嘅風險存在。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">[b]麻煩大家亞馬遜唔好再用殘體字 可以用英文</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n網購筆集中討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1856697/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1856697/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc20b7880fa07a4cc07881bfb8b255e992ec335","tid":1856891,"uid":45505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T01:28:48.000Z","msg":"做乜今日條街咁多kf90嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bb74e05d4e466c5614130d848432dc9fd41b277","tid":1856891,"uid":24378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T01:35:32.000Z","msg":"臭罩cut 咗單<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19fd368d03642d42692c2ed25204494f41662761","tid":1856891,"uid":9752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"q